<i>noun</i>: 자성 [자성], 성찰 [성찰] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자성 [자성]</dt><br>
<dd>reflection; self-examination</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 태도나 행동을 반성함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of reflecting on one's own attitude or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성찰 [성찰]</dt><br>
<dd>introspection; self-examination</dd><br>
<dd>스스로를 반성하고 살핌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of reflecting on oneself.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>